data.description: Welcome to your dream oasis! This stunning ranch-style home is the epitome of luxury and comfort, nestled on a generous homesite that offers ample space for your every desire. Boasting a plethora of builder upgrades and a magnificent front porch and rear patio, this property is the epitome of fine living. Don't miss the additional parking on the side with the extended driveway. This home has been meticulously designed with an array of premium builder upgrades, making it the epitome of contemporary elegance. From high-end fixtures to top-quality materials, no expense has been spared. The open-concept floor plan creates an inviting and harmonious living space, ideal for entertaining or simply relaxing with family and friends. The heart of the home, the gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, complete with state-of-the-art appliances, granite countertops, and a large island. Prepare delicious meals while being the center of attention. Your private retreat awaits in the luxurious master suite. Pamper yourself in the spa-like ensuite bathroom and walk-in closet. Upstairs you will find a spacious bonus room, ready to make it your own. Use it as an office, second living area or work out space! Step outside onto the extensive rear patio that was upgraded to add additional outdoor entertaining space and experience the ultimate in outdoor living. This expansive space is perfect for al fresco dining, hosting BBQs, or simply enjoying the tranquil surroundings. The vast homesite provides plenty of room for endless possibilities. Don't miss the opportunity to make this remarkable ranch home your own. This home is USDA eligible, please reach out for more information.
